These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There 5 different types of food: lime, peach, strawberry, lemon, cucumber
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: may, june, october, july, march
City: hamburg, london, paris, hannover, prague
5 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, lizard, rabbit, rat
 1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 4. the person eating strawberry is the person eating strawberry##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 6. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 8. the person eating lemon is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person eating lemon is on the far right##1
10. the person eating lime is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
11. the person eating cucumber is between the person traveling to london and the person who's birthday is in march##2
12. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
13. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Food      | lime        | peach | cucumber     | strawberry   | lemon |
| Birthday   | october     | june      | july | march   | may    |
| City   | hannover  | london     | hamburg | paris | prague  |
| Pet           | chinchilla | lizard      | rat     | rabbit   | bird     |

