.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
5 different games are played: billiard, monopoly, whist, bridge, scrabble
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, d&b, disco, r&b, techno
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, january, april, august, october
There 5 different types of food: mango, peas, lettuce, pepper, cabbage
 1. the person eating cabbage is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of techno is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 4. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 5. the person eating peas is between the person who's birthday is in june and the fan of techno##2
 6. the person eating pepper is the person playing monopoly##1
 7. the fan of country is on the left of the person eating mango##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
10. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
11. the person who's birthday is in april is the person playing whist##1
12. the person eating peas is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Game         | bridge | billiard | scrabble    | monopoly  | whist    |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | d&b       | disco      | country | r&b        |
| Birthday   | october   | january     | june    | august  | april     |
| Food     | lettuce    | peas | cabbage | pepper | mango |

