.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
City: london, miami, colone, paris, hamburg
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: aconite, sunflower, zinnia, azalea, amaryllis
The people use 5 different means of transport: subway, quad-bike, taxi, bike, bus
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who growssunflower##1
 2. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
 3. the person who growsazalea is in the middle##1
 4. the person traveling to london is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 8. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 9. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
10. the person driving the subway is the person traveling to paris##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
13. the person driving the bus is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing     | puzzles   | filmmaking   | rock-climbing |
| City   | hamburg  | miami | london | paris | colone        |
| Flower   | zinnia      | sunflower      | azalea       | amaryllis       | aconite       |
| Transport         | quad-bike | bus  | bike    | subway    | taxi        |

