.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, swisher, old-henry, ritmeester, alhambra
5 different pets are kept: mouse, turtle, rat, horse, cat
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: scientific, romance, zombie, drama, thriller
There are 5 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, japanese, pakistani
 1. the egyptian is on the far left##1
 2. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 3. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
 4. the pakistani is between the person watching drama movies and the ritmeester-smoker##2
 5. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 6. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the indonesian##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 8. the owner of the cat is the person watching romance movies##1
 9. the person watching thriller movies is in the middle##1
10. the person watching drama movies is the british##1
11. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
12. the british is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
13. the person watching romance movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Cigar          | alhambra  | old-henry     | ritmeester   | swisher     | havana |
| Pet         | cat | mouse    | rat  | horse | turtle   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance        | scientific    | thriller     | zombie     | drama    |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | indonesian | japanese | pakistani | british   |

