The people have 5 different hobbies: camping, dancing, magic-tricks, video-games, card-games
The people use 5 different means of transport: skateboard, subway, bus, tram, jet-ski
 1. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is between the person driving the subway and the oliveros-smoker##2
 5. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
11. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
12. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
13. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
