House: cottage, ranch-style, modern, craftsman, futuristic
 1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the fan of country##1
 2. the modern house is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 3. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 4. the fan of jazz is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 5. the futuristic house is on the right of the cottage house##1
 6. the fan of blues is between the person watching zombie movies and the ranch-style house##2
 7. the modern house is the owner of the rat##1
 8. the owner of the snake is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
10. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the ranch-style house##2
12. the fan of country is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
13. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
| Music-Genre      | soul  | blues      | jazz   | country   | rock   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie    | thriller   | sports   | mystery | family     |
