 9. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
11. the person drinking mirinda is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
12. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
