House: modern, futuristic, victorian, art-deco, wooden
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, drawing, reading, traveling, video-games
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: house, ambient, dubstep, d&b, salsa
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, chaman, havana, siglo, baccarat
 1. the fan of salsa is between the chaman-smoker and the fan of ambient##2
 2. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 3. the futuristic house is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the modern house is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 5. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 7. the blend-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
10. the fan of dubstep is on the far left##1
11. the havana-smoker is between the fan of dubstep and the person who's hobby is reading##2
12. the art-deco house is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
13. the victorian house is on the left of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| House    | victorian       | art-deco    | wooden | futuristic  | modern        |
| Hobby       | video-games | card-games | reading  | traveling | drawing    |
| Music-Genre       | dubstep        | d&b   | ambient  | salsa   | house |
| Cigar   | siglo       | havana      | baccarat      | blend | chaman  |

