.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, helicopter, skateboard, bus, jet-ski
5 different pets are kept: goat, hamster, horse, bird, lizard
There are 5 different nationalities: russian, nigerian, turkish, american, mexican
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, blues, hip-hop, house, trance
 1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the nigerian##1
 2. the owner of the bird is between the turkish and the owner of the horse##2
 3. the person driving the bus is the owner of the bird##1
 4. the mexican is on the right of the fan of house##1
 5. the russian is in the middle##1
 6. the person driving the bus is between the owner of the lizard and the fan of blues##2
 7. the fan of house is the person driving the skateboard##1
 8. the person driving the motorbike is the fan of hip-hop##1
 9. the fan of ambient is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
10. the owner of the goat is on the right of the turkish##1
11. the owner of the horse is the nigerian##1
12. the american is on the far left##1
13. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Transport      | motorbike      | helicopter         | bus      | skateboard | jet-ski     |
| Pet           | hamster | horse | bird | lizard    | goat  |
| Nationality   | american  | nigerian    | russian | turkish    | mexican |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | blues        | ambient   | house    | trance     |

