.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: chestnut, apricot, coral, ebony, brown
There 5 different types of food: spinach, plum, corn, cucumber, pineapple
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: disaster, western, time-travel, drama, family
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, car, helicopter, jet-ski, ship
 1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating plum##1
 3. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching western movies is between the person eating spinach and the person watching disaster movies##2
 6. the person eating spinach is on the far left##1
 7. the person who likes coral is between the person driving the airplane and the person who likes brown##2
 8. the person who likes apricot is between the person who likes ebony and the person who likes chestnut##2
 9. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
10. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Color         | brown  | coral | ebony   | apricot      | chestnut |
| Food   | spinach   | cucumber    | plum | pineapple | corn      |
| Movie-Genre           | time-travel | western    | disaster       | drama     | family      |
| Transport     | helicopter | ship        | airplane  | car        | jet-ski    |

