.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: blood-red, green, yellow, emerald, lilac
The people use 5 different means of transport: subway, trike, car, quad-bike, roller
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, blues, electronic, reggae, rock
5 different pets are kept: lizard, rabbit, horse, rat, pony
 1. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 2. the person driving the roller is between the owner of the rat and the fan of rock##2
 3. the fan of rock is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 4. the person driving the roller is the fan of ambient##1
 5. the fan of ambient is between the owner of the pony and the fan of electronic##2
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 7. the person driving the car is the fan of reggae##1
 8. the person who likes emerald is the fan of blues##1
 9. the owner of the lizard is the fan of blues##1
10. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
11. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who likes green##1
12. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Color         | yellow    | lilac  | green  | blood-red      | emerald |
| Transport   | trike    | roller   | quad-bike | car | subway   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | ambient    | rock    | reggae       | blues         |
| Pet   | rat  | rabbit | pony    | horse     | lizard      |

 